Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H232A96&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!\NPeople are Turning into Trees!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On that day I was kicking a stone down a\Ncountry road where canola flowers bloomed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Birds were flying high in the sky\NBirds were flying high in the sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why don't we have lunch here?\N-Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry...\N-Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I can hear human voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Water, please...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's it coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that, daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like people, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the trees talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... help us...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's unbelievable!\NAre they haunted!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go back, darling!\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is Alseides!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alseides?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And what... do you\Nwant with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna join GOD's guinea pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Darling!\N-Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Darling!\N-Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy! Sis!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there?\NHelp me! Anybody!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we stop him, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, everyone\Nin Japan will be a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My experiment's already a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your experiment is a failure! Their bodies\Nmay be wood, but their minds are still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cannot suppress their minds,\Nthen your plan must be postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Supreme Commander--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alseides!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have new orders: Eliminate that\Nboy before the day is done. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there!\NBring me that brat already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? People becoming trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So a monster turned this\Nkid's family into trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, you think GOD might be behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! You think GOD\Ncan turn people into trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was probably daydreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, rescue my daddy and mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Hyouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fine... C'mon, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Pass my jacket?\N-Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we tag along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it was this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Hyouta's just over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thanks!\N-Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Take care, ok?\N-Ok! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're\Ntaking this kid seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here! This is where\Nthey got turned into trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything that\Nlooks like a human tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird, I'm sure\Nthis was the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're really sure?\N-I told you he dreamt it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get to?\NYou know better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But... didn't you get turned into trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Were\Nyou daydreaming again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm just glad it turned out ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you so much.\N-It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Just like I said. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't fool me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me, but stay out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't look well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They turned into trees again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're gonna join them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come on, Takeshi!\N-Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! That brat's slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No one learns GOD's\Nsecrets and lives! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew GOD were behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Jin Keisuke's here! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, make like a tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Rider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the brat to live, drop\Nyour weapon and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got 'til I count\Nthree to answer, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't survive a fall from that height.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Two...!\N-Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoying the view, Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hold onto him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're going\Nback on your word?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to enjoy every\Nsecond of your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've beaten Jin Keisuke! Now to take\NApollo Geist's place as senior officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Apollo Geist.\NI've finished Jin Keisuke off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! The X Rider\Ncan't die so easiy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I can defeat the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to prove\Nit, then! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-That way!\N-Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-You ok, Keisuke!?\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, put the fire out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! Still alive, Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alseides... This really\Nisn't bad for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite the interesting little\Nshow you're putting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Jin Keisuke can't lift a finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye to Jin Keisuke forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke is dead...\Nand now it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Kill me first, if you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's still alive!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, look after Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the X Rider would\Ngive up! We lost him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the brakes! What are\Nyou doing!? Stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, today we settle\Nthis! Let's go, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Apollo Geist.\NLet me handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not worthy of\Nfacing the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I owe him!\NLet me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're that confident,\Nthen have at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This time you die, X Rider!\NHave a taste of my whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for breaking my whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Crown Splitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alright! I'm so glad!\NBut what happened to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Daddy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi! You're safe\Ntoo! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mommy!\N-What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But what changed you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't have a clue either...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider beat the\Nmonster and broke the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What in the world\Nare you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, you see--\N-It's like this--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You got turned into\Ntrees too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous! You can't just do\Nwhat you like without telling us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry!\N-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We should apologise for putting\Nyou through so much too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, X Rider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider has crushed GOD's\Nawful plan to turn people into trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have another plot in store.\NWill the X Rider be up to the challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for us, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A black cat spreads a mysterious virus,\Ntransforming city residents into cat-people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware the black cat!\NIt's an agent of GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Scary! It's GOD's Ghost Cat Plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.21,0:24:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.21,0:24:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider